  <official_title>Selection of CD34+THY-1 Positive Cells From Peripheral Blood Cells Procured for Autologous Hematopoietic Support Following High Dose Treatment With BCNU, Cyclophosphamide &amp; Cisplatin for Stage IV Breast Cancer &amp; Limited Prior Treatment</official_title>
