  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluate the feasibility and safety of autologous transplantation of CD34+Thy-1+
      hematopoietic stem cells afer high dose marrow ablative chemotherapy in patients with breast
      cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
